What could I do?

18
00:02:28,370 --> 00:02:30,770
Isn't it good enough that I'm here with you?

19
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:32,450
Anyway, you like me,

20
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:33,240
right?

21
