366
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:08,860
Xiaofei,

367
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:10,480
Xing is a good man.

368
00:14:10,510 --> 00:14:11,630
He cares about you.

369
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:14,330
